org.pipservices.runtime.build

Class ComponentFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pipservices.runtime.build.ComponentFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IComponentFactory
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultFactory

    public class ComponentFactory
extends Object
implements IComponentFactory
    Factory for microservice components. It registers component classes, locates classes by descriptors and creates component instances. It also supports inheritance from other factories.
    Since:
    2016-06-09
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Sergey Seroukhov
